description:
I do not take full credit for this code. Base code comes from style 19950 by user 26447.

1) Removes the top navigation, footer, and right column, so this style is good for those who simply post and read posts made by anyone they follow.
2) Color and style changes.
3) You can replace the header in this section. Replace the url with the url of your desired header. Make sure it's at least 300px high and the width of your screen:

#dashboard_index #header {
  position: absolute !important;
  top: 0px !important;
  left: 0px !important; 
  height: 300px !important;
  width: 100% !important;
  background: url('http://i46.tinypic.com/sdp8au.png') center !important;
}



Here are a couple screencaps to give you an idea (they're too large to upload thumbnails here):

Before: http://img254.imageshack.us/img254/9166/tumblr1265026978367.png

After: http://yfrog.com/59tumblr1265026988098p

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("tumblr.com") {
* {
  -moz-border-radius: 0px !important;
}
#dashboard_index, #dashboard_index div.l-header, #dashboard_index #container, #dashboard_index div.l-content, #dashboard_index #dashboard_edit_post {
  background: #262626 !important;
}
#dashboard_index div.l-header {
  position: absolute !important;
  top: 0px !important;
  left: 0px !important; 
  height: 300px !important;
  width: 100% !important;
  background: url('http://i46.tinypic.com/sdp8au.png') center !important;
}
#dashboard_index #new_post_notice_container {
  position: absolute !important;
  top: 210px !important; 
  left: -10px !important;
}
#dashboard_index #logo {
  top: 250px !important;
  left: 10px !important;
  opacity: 0.7 !important;
}
#dashboard_index #nav {
  top: 120px !important;
  right: 50px !important;
  display: none !important;
}
#dashboard_index #search_query, #dashboard_index .search_icon, #dashboard_index #tip{
  display: none !important;
}

#dashboard_index #right_column {
  width: 0 !important;
  height: 0 !important;
  display: none !important;
}

#dashboard_index #left_column, #right_column {background-color: transparent !important;}

div.l-content.l-content.l-content {
  margin-top: 255px !important;
  margin-left: 100px !important;
}
#dashboard_index .arrow {
  display:none !important;
}

ol#posts li blockquote {
    margin: 0 !important;
}

#dashboard_index .avatar {
  border: none !important;
  border-left: 3px solid #0e0f14 !important;
  border-bottom: 3px solid #0e0f14 !important;
  -moz-border-radius: 8px !important;
}
#dashboard_index .post {
  border: 4px solid #0e0f14 !important;
  color: #161616 !important;
  margin-top: 25px !important;
}

#dashboard_index #new_post .avatar ,#dashboard_index #new_post .arrow{
  border: 1px solid #0e0f14 !important;
  -moz-border-radius: 8px !important;
}
#dashboard_index .new_post {
  border: 4px solid #0e0f14 !important;
  margin-bottom: 50px !important;
}

#dashboard_index .notes {
  border: 1px dashed #0e0f14 !important;
  background: #e7e9ee !important;
  padding-left: 10px !important;
  padding-right: 10px !important;
  padding-bottom: 5px !important;
}

#dashboard_index .post_title {
  color: #787a87 !important;
  font-weight: bold !important;
}
#dashboard_index .post_title a {
  color: #787a87 !important;
  font-weight: normal !important;
}

#dashboard_index .notification {
  border: 1px solid #0e0f14 !important;
  background: #555 !important;
  color: #262626 !important;
}
#dashboard_index .notification a {
  color: #262626 !important;
}

#dashboard_index img.permalink {
  height: 0 !important;
  width: 0 !important;
  /* these numbers match the new image's dimensions */
  padding-left: 15px !important;
  padding-top: 15px !important;
  margin-top: 2px;
  background: url('http://i47.tinypic.com/22x9gg.png') no-repeat !important;
}

#dashboard_index #next_page_link, #previous_page_link {
  background: none !important;
  color: #555 !important;
}
#dashboard_index #next_page_link, #previous_page_link a {
  color: #555 !important;
}

#dashboard_index #footer, #dashboard_index #footer a {
  color: #fff !important;
  display: none !important;
}

}
